PrecisAmendment to the DESIGNATED PROVISIONS REGULATIONS increasing the number of offences punishable by means of an administrative monetary penalty in respect of the Aerodrome Security Regulations, raising the maximum penalty for these offences and those shown under the Air Carrier Security Regulations, and setting out a new schedule showing the maximum penalty for each provision for an individual as opposed to a corporation.
